@Article{pmid11565518,
   Author="Brenner, B. M.  and Cooper, M. E.  and de Zeeuw, D.  and Keane, W. F.  and Mitch, W. E.  and Parving, H. H.  and Remuzzi, G.  and Snapinn, S. M.  and Zhang, Z.  and Shahinfar, S. ",
