   Title="{{C}omparative effect of lercanidipine, felodipine, and nifedipine {G}{I}{T}{S} on blood pressure and heart rate in patients with mild to moderate arterial hypertension: the {L}ercanidipine in {A}dults ({L}{E}{A}{D}) {S}tudy}",
