   Title="{{V}on {W}illebrand factor, soluble {P}-selectin, and target organ damage in hypertension: a substudy of the {A}nglo-{S}candinavian {C}ardiac {O}utcomes {T}rial ({A}{S}{C}{O}{T})}",
   Journal="Hypertension",
